      "text": "items: FavouriteItem[]  { id, type, qty(min1), toppingIds[] }\nsets:  FavouriteSet[]   { id(UUID), name, createdAt, items[] }\nwrites: addItem · removeItem · updateQty(Math.max(1)) ·\n        addSet(snapshot) · renameSet · deleteSet · toggleFav\nPERSISTED — whole {items,sets} survives reload  (favourites.ts:43-93)",
