      "text": "handleAddAllToCart (page.tsx:97-122) → addToCart × N\nhandleApplySet     (sets:72-98)      → addToCart × set\naddSet (save:73-75) → snapshot items[] → sets[] (persisted)\n→ cart → /menu TableConfirmModal / checkout → POST /orders\n(normalised by lib/order-payload.ts at submit)",
