      "index": "z00023",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "• stale-favourite prune = side effect of catalog reads, not a push: admin deletes product → pruned from a guest's favourites only after that guest reopens list + 5-min TTL refreshes (pull+TTL, no push)\n• cart is shared mutable state: \"Add all\"/\"apply set\" APPENDS — applying two sets gives both (addItem additive)",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "• stale-favourite prune = side effect of catalog reads, not a push: admin deletes product → pruned from a guest's favourites only after that guest reopens list + 5-min TTL refreshes (pull+TTL, no push)\n• cart is shared mutable state: \"Add all\"/\"apply set\" APPENDS — applying two sets gives both (addItem additive)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
