      "frameId": null,
      "text": "1. route nav   → ShopLoading: centered orange spinner (whole (shop) shell) — loading.tsx:1-7\n2. page mount  → NO Suspense boundary, NO page-level fallback (no useSearchParams)\n3. 2 useQuery  → ['products-all'] + ['combos'], both default [] → page renders from store immediately, items pop in silently",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
