      "originalText": "a hearted dish was removed from the menu → absent from GET /products payload.\nresolvedItems drops it (if(!p)return[]); mount useEffect (runs once both loaded) → removeItem + toast \"Một số món không còn phục vụ…\". No BE call drove it — pull + 5-min TTL.",
