      "index": "z00010",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "products            (GET /products · is_available=1, not soft-deleted)\n  id · name · base_price · image_url · is_available\nproduct_toppings    (GetToppingsByProductID per product)\n  product_id · topping_id · price\ncombos              (GET /combos · ListCombosAvailable)\n  id · name · base_price · image_url\ncombo_items         (GetComboItems per combo)\n  combo_id · product_id · quantity   ← ids only\n\nfavourite gone ⇔ its id absent from these payloads (auto-prune)",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "products            (GET /products · is_available=1, not soft-deleted)\n  id · name · base_price · image_url · is_available\nproduct_toppings    (GetToppingsByProductID per product)\n  product_id · topping_id · price\ncombos              (GET /combos · ListCombosAvailable)\n  id · name · base_price · image_url\ncombo_items         (GetComboItems per combo)\n  combo_id · product_id · quantity   ← ids only\n\nfavourite gone ⇔ its id absent from these payloads (auto-prune)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
